    <h1>London</h1>
    <p>London, the capital city of the United Kingdom, is one of the world’s most dynamic and historic cities. Located along the River Thames, London is known for its rich cultural heritage, iconic landmarks, and global influence in politics, finance, art, and fashion. Famous attractions such as Big Ben, the Houses of Parliament, Buckingham Palace, the Tower of London, and the London Eye draw millions of visitors each year.</p>
    <p>The city is also a melting pot of cultures, with people from all over the world contributing to its diverse food, music, and traditions. From the historic streets of Westminster to the modern skyline of Canary Wharf, London perfectly blends old-world charm with contemporary innovation. It remains a global center of education, creativity, and progress — a place where history and modern life coexist beautifully.</p>



    